To those who choose to support the development of SIC:

Your sponsorship is directly converted into time, stability, and forward momentum.
You help transform SIC from a promising system into a fully realized language capable of serving real-world environments and serious engineering needs.

Every contribution — large or small — strengthens:

the rigor of the design

the quality of the implementation

the pace of development

the reach of the documentation

the longevity of the project


Thank you for supporting disciplined engineering.
Thank you for supporting clarity over chaos.
Thank you for supporting SIC.

— R.P. Syndicate Laboratories
